Getopt::Clade version 0.0.1

This is a placeholder for the actual Getopt::Clade module, which will be 
released in the next month or two (around September 2005).


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

None.


